  hiding commit ac23eb7fe089 "B"
  1 changeset hidden
  removing bookmark 'revive1' (was at: ac23eb7fe089)
  1 bookmark removed

  $ sl log -Gr 'all()' -T '{desc|firstline} {bookmarks}'
  @  B2 branch2 branch3
  │
  o  A

